Dell

Zookeeper Start
 sudo /usr/share/zookeeper/bin/zkServer.sh start-foreground
Check Zookeeper
 telnet localhost 2181 
 ruok


Kafka
https://hevodata.com/blog/how-to-install-kafka-on-ubuntu/#java
https://michaeljohnpena.com/blog/kafka-wsl2/
Zookeeper-server-start: $KAFKA_HOME/bin/zookeeper-server-start.sh $KAFKA_HOME/config/zookeeper.properties
Kafka-Server-start: $KAFKA_HOME/bin/kafka-server-start.sh $KAFKA_HOME/config/server.properties
Kafka-Producer-start: $KAFKA_HOME/bin/kafka-console-producer.sh --topic quickstart-events --bootstrap-server localhost:9092
Kafka-Consumer-start: $KAFKA_HOME/bin/kafka-console-consumer.sh --topic quickstart-events --bootstrap-server localhost:9092
Create-topics: $KAFKA_HOME/bin/kafka-topics.sh --create --topic topic_name --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

